author: Scott Manley
description:
All the deep space updates from the last two weeks, and it's been eventful for all sorts of reasons, SpaceX is cleaning up after Booster 18 failed, Russia needs to fix its launch site. China almost recovers a rocket booster and the US government recovers the NASA administrator candidate who was ready to go earlier this year.

Follow me on Twitter for more updates:
https://twitter.com/DJSnM

I have a discord server where I regularly turn up:
https://discord.gg/zStmKbM

If you really like what I do you can support me directly through Patreon
https://www.patreon.com/scottmanley
